<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset - Uttara University</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .alert-warning {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 2px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #856404;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .alert-warning strong {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .intro-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .otp-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: white;
        }

        .otp-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: block;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .otp-code {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            word-break: break-all;
        }

        .otp-validity {
            font-size: 12px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .security-section {
            background: #e8f5e9;
            border: 1px solid #81c784;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-left: 4px solid #4caf50;
        }

        .security-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2e7d32;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .security-title::before {
            content: "🔒";
            margin-right: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .security-point {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            padding-left: 20px;
            position: relative;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .security-point:before {
            content: "✓";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #4caf50;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .security-point:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .instructions-section {
            background: #f0f4ff;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
        }

        .instructions-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #333;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .instructions-title::before {
            content: "📋";
            margin-right: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .instruction-step {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            padding-left: 28px;
            position: relative;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .instruction-step:before {
            content: attr(data-step);
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            width: 22px;
            height: 22px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .instruction-step:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .danger-section {
            background: #ffebee;
            border: 1px solid #ef5350;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-left: 4px solid #f44336;
        }

        .danger-title {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #c62828;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .danger-title::before {
            content: "⚠️";
            margin-right: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .danger-text {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #b71c1c;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 25px 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .footer-link {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .support-text {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: #e0e0e0;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                border-radius: 0;
            }

            .content {
                padding: 25px 20px;
            }

            .header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }

            .header h1 {
                font-size: 22px;
            }

            .otp-code {
                font-size: 24px;
                letter-spacing: 4px;
                padding: 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🔑 Password Reset</h1>
            <p>Secure Your Account</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <!-- Greeting -->
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello <strong>
                    <%= name %>
                </strong>,
            </div>

            <!-- Alert Warning -->
            <div class="alert-warning">
                <strong>Password Reset Request</strong>
                We received a request to reset your password. If you didn't make this request, please ignore this email
                and your account will remain secure.
            </div>

            <!-- Introduction -->
            <div class="intro-text">
                To reset your password, please use the One-Time Password (OTP) below. This code will expire in
                <strong>5 minutes</strong> for your security.
            </div>

            <!-- OTP Section -->
            <div class="otp-section">
                <span class="otp-label">Your One-Time Password</span>
                <div class="otp-code">
                    <%= otp %>
                </div>
                <div class="otp-validity">
                    ⏱️ Valid for 5 minutes only
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Instructions -->
            <div class="instructions-section">
                <div class="instructions-title">How to Reset Your Password</div>
                <div class="instruction-step" data-step="1">Visit the password reset page on Uttara University portal
                </div>
                <div class="instruction-step" data-step="2">Enter your email address</div>
                <div class="instruction-step" data-step="3">Enter the OTP code shown above</div>
                <div class="instruction-step" data-step="4">Create a new secure password</div>
                <div class="instruction-step" data-step="5">Confirm your new password and submit</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Security Tips -->
            <div class="security-section">
                <div class="security-title">Security Tips</div>
                <div class="security-point">Never share your OTP with anyone</div>
                <div class="security-point">Use a strong, unique password with uppercase, lowercase, numbers, and
                    symbols</div>
                <div class="security-point">Avoid using personal information in your password</div>
                <div class="security-point">Change your password regularly for better security</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Danger Section -->
            <div class="danger-section">
                <div class="danger-title">Important Notice</div>
                <div class="danger-text">
                    This OTP will automatically expire in 10 minutes. After expiration, you'll need to request a new
                    password reset. Do not share this code with anyone.
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Support Information -->
            <div class="intro-text" style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px;">
                <strong>Need Assistance?</strong><br>
                If you didn't request this password reset or need help, please contact our support team at <a
                    href="mailto:support@uttarauniversity.edu" style="color: #667eea;">support@uttarauniversity.edu</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <strong>Uttara University</strong><br>
            <span style="color: #999;">© 2026 Uttara University. All rights reserved.</span><br>
            <div style="margin-top: 15px;">
                <a href="#" class="footer-link">Privacy Policy</a> |
                <a href="#" class="footer-link">Terms of Service</a> |
                <a href="#" class="footer-link">Contact Us</a>
            </div>
            <div class="support-text">
                This is an automated security email. Please do not reply directly to this message.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>